<h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Baloo Thambi 2&quot;, cursive; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 39px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); margin: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Băng Bảo Vệ Khớp Cổ Ch&acirc;n 360&ordm; BCC01 &ndash; VNSPORT</span></h2>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Baloo Thambi 2&quot;, cursive; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14pt; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif; vertical-align: baseline;">Việc ph&ograve;ng tr&aacute;nh chấn thương khu vực khớp cổ ch&acirc;n, mắt c&aacute; ch&acirc;n rất quan trọng, v&igrave; nếu bị chấn thương vị tr&iacute; n&agrave;y sẽ ảnh hưởng rất lớn tới việc đi lại, di chuyển sinh hoạt thường ng&agrave;y.</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Baloo Thambi 2&quot;, cursive; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14pt; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif; vertical-align: baseline;">V&igrave; vậy, việc lựa chọn cho m&igrave;nh một phụ kiện hỗ trợ v&agrave; ph&ograve;ng tr&aacute;nh chấn thương đặc biệt l&agrave; ph&ograve;ng tr&aacute;nh chấn thương khu vực khớp cổ ch&acirc;n, mắt c&aacute; ch&acirc;n l&agrave; rất quan trọng.&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: underline;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="https://vnsport.com.vn/bang-bao-ve-khop-co-tay-360o-bct01-vn-sport/" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 1s ease 0s; outline: 0px;" title="Băng bảo vệ khớp cổ chân">Băng bảo vệ khớp cổ ch&acirc;n</a></strong></span></span>&nbsp;ph&ugrave; hợp cho c&aacute;c m&ocirc;n thể thao như tennis, b&oacute;ng chuyền, cầu l&ocirc;ng, đ&aacute; banh, boxing, điền kinh, nhảy cao,..</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Baloo Thambi 2&quot;, cursive; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">
	<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14pt; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif; vertical-align: baseline;">H&atilde;y ph&ograve;ng tr&aacute;nh chấn thương trước khi phải điều trị bằng c&aacute;ch lựa chọn cho m&igrave;nh một phụ kiện thể thao ph&ugrave; hợp, hiệu quả v&agrave; thời trang. T&igrave;m hiểu xem&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: underline;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="https://vnsport.com.vn/bang-bao-ve-khop-co-tay-360o-bct01-vn-sport/" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 1s ease 0s; outline: 0px;" title="băng bảo vệ khớp chân&nbsp;360º">băng bảo vệ khớp ch&acirc;n&nbsp;360&ordm;</a></strong></span></span>&nbsp; BCC01 c&oacute; đặc điểm như thế n&agrave;o nh&eacute;.</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Baloo Thambi 2&quot;, cursive; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;">
	<img alt="" class="size-full wp-image-5513 aligncenter lazy-loaded" data-="" data-lazy-type="image" data-srcset="" height="2348" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px" src="https://vnsport.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bang-co-chan-360-vnsport-1.jpg" srcset="https://vnsport.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bang-co-chan-360-vnsport-1.jpg 750w, https://vnsport.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bang-co-chan-360-vnsport-1-491x1536.jpg 491w, https://vnsport.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bang-co-chan-360-vnsport-1-654x2048.jpg 654w, https://vnsport.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bang-co-chan-360-vnsport-1-600x1878.jpg 600w, https://vnsport.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/bang-co-chan-360-vnsport-1-64x200.jpg 64w" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(224, 224, 224); vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto 10px; padding: 2px; font: inherit; display: block; max-width: 100%; clear: both; height: auto !important;" width="750" /></p>
